            <abstract>
                <p>The text of Vita of St Mercurius, <cit>
                        <quote>of which, for the moment, only the Geez version is known. It is an
                            abbreviated recension, made narratively consistent with the usual scheme
                            of the Gadl. </quote>
                    </cit> This text is classified in <bibl>
                        <ptr target="bm:Proverbio1993PassioMercuri"/><citedRange unit="page"
                            >459</citedRange>
                    </bibl>as 'recension c'. This text is known to be assigned for <date ref="ethiocal:Hedar25">25th of Ḫǝdār</date>.</p>
            </abstract>
